---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Ariff Afandi - Cloud Solutions Engineer | Azure Security | MIT Student"
  description="Professional portfolio showcasing Azure cloud security expertise, technical projects, and cybersecurity solutions. MIT Cybersecurity Graduate Student."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Ariff Afandi</h1>
      <h2>Cloud Solutions Engineer | Azure Security Specialist</h2>
      <p>Transforming cloud infrastructure with security-first architecture and innovative Azure solutions. Currently pursuing Cybersecurity at MIT.</p>
      <div class="hero-links">
        <a href="#projects" class="btn-primary">View Projects</a>
        <a href="#about" class="btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Projects Grid -->
  <section id="projects" class="projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Featured Azure Projects</h2>
      <p>Explore my technical expertise through these specialized Azure implementations</p>
      
      <div class="projects-grid">
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Azure Virtual Desktop</h3>
          <p>Enterprise-grade virtual desktop infrastructure with enhanced security controls and optimized performance.</p>
          <a href="https://avd.aglobaltec.com" class="project-link" target="_blank">Explore AVD →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Azure AI Services</h3>
          <p>Intelligent cloud solutions leveraging Microsoft AI and machine learning capabilities for business transformation.</p>
          <a href="https://ai.aglobaltec.com" class="project-link" target="_blank">Explore AI →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Azure Backup Solutions</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive backup and disaster recovery strategies ensuring business continuity and data protection.</p>
          <a href="https://backup.aglobaltec.com" class="project-link" target="_blank">Explore Backup →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Azure Governance</h3>
          <p>Strategic cloud governance frameworks with policy implementation and compliance automation.</p>
          <a href="https://governance.aglobaltec.com" class="project-link" target="_blank">Explore Governance →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>As a Cloud Solutions Engineer specializing in Azure security, I bring a unique blend of technical expertise and strategic thinking to cloud infrastructure challenges. My experience spans enterprise-level implementations, security architecture, and innovative problem-solving.</p>
          
          <p>Currently advancing my expertise through MIT's Cybersecurity program, I'm passionate about developing secure, scalable cloud solutions that drive business value while maintaining the highest security standards.</p>
          
          <div class="expertise">
            <h3>Core Expertise</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Azure Security Architecture</li>
              <li>Cloud Infrastructure Design</li>
              <li>DevSecOps Implementation</li>
              <li>Compliance & Governance</li>
              <li>Identity & Access Management</li>
              <li>Threat Detection & Response</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section id="contact" class="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>Interested in collaborating or discussing cloud security solutions? Let's connect.</p>
      
      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com" class="contact-link">
          <span>Email</span>
          <span>ariff@aglobaltec.com</span>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ariff-afandi" class="contact-link" target="_blank">
          <span>LinkedIn</span>
          <span>Professional Profile</span>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/a-ariff" class="contact-link" target="_blank">
          <span>GitHub</span>
          <span>Technical Portfolio</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0078d4 0%, #005a9e 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 100px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .hero-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .hero-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: #0078d4;
  }
  
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid white;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: white;
    color: #0078d4;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .projects {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .projects h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .projects > .container > p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .project-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .project-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .project-card h3 {
    color: #0078d4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  
  .project-card p {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .project-link {
    color: #0078d4;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .project-link:hover {
    color: #005a9e;
  }
  
  .about {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .about h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .expertise {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  
  .expertise h3 {
    color: #0078d4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  
  .expertise ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .expertise li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #555;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .expertise li:before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #0078d4;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  
  .contact {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .contact h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .contact > .container > p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .contact-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .contact-link {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .contact-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .contact-link span:first-child {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0078d4;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .contact-link span:last-child {
    color: #666;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .hero-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .expertise ul {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
